Emily Hart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Hart 0 Emily Anne Hart (born May 2, 1986) is an American actress and voice actress. She is the younger sister of actress Melissa Joan Hart. She is best known for her roles as Sabrina Spellman in Sabrina: The Animated Series and Amanda Wiccan in Sabrina the Teenage Witch.
